    "en": {
      "title": "Patients returned due to lack of diesel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two patients who were taken by ambulance from Puttalam Aadar Hospital to Colombo National Hospital, Maharagama Cancer Hospital for further treatment were taken back to Puttalam Hospital due to diesel problems.",
        "While fuel was being distributed to the Puttalam Aadar Hospital at the filling station in Diladia, the hospital authorities are facing serious problems due to non-supply of fuel to the ambulance carrying the patients."
      ],
